quran[3]{c,v,t,f}:
  2,7,"Allâh has set a seal on their hearts and on their hearing, (i.e. they are closed from accepting Allâh’s Guidance), and on their eyes there is a covering. Theirs will be a great torment."
  2,8,"And of mankind, there are some (hypocrites) who say: "
  2,9,"They (think to) deceive Allâh and those who believe, while they only deceive themselves, and perceive (it) not!"